The demonstrates a hello world project with: 
- jersey [http://jersey.java.net]
- metrics [http://metrics.codahale.com]



To run sample,

1) Build war file
./gradlew war
2) Deploy war file to web container
3) Open browser to:
/jersey-helloworld/


There is a metric counter around each hit on "hello" and "echo".
Navigate to the metrics to see the counters.
